<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MOCHILA • Tipos de Sistemas Operacionais</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e2937 0%, #334155 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        .card {
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.4);
        }
        .icon-circle {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        
        <!-- Botão Voltar -->
        <a href="index.html" 
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-violet-300 mb-8">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Voltar para a Mochila
        </a>

        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">📟 Tipos de Sistemas Operacionais</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">Cada tipo foi feito para um objetivo diferente</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

            <!-- Desktop -->
            <div class="card bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-8">
                <div class="icon-circle bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 mx-auto mb-6">💻</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-2">Desktop</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-blue-400 mb-6">Computadores Pessoais</p>
                <p class="text-center mb-6"><strong>Ex: Microsoft Windows, macOS, Linux</strong></p>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li>✅ Usado em PCs e Notebooks</li>
                    <li>✅ Foco no usuário final</li>
                    <li>✅ Multitarefa e interface gráfica</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Mobile -->
            <div class="card bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-8">
                <div class="icon-circle bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 mx-auto mb-6">📱</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-2">Mobile</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-green-400 mb-6">Dispositivos Móveis</p>
                <p class="text-center mb-6"><strong>Ex: Android, iOS</strong></p>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li>✅ Smartphones e Tablets</li>
                    <li>✅ Foco em apps e mobilidade</li>
                    <li>✅ Otimizado para tela touch</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Servidores -->
            <div class="card bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-8">
                <div class="icon-circle bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 mx-auto mb-6">🌐</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-2">Servidores</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-purple-400 mb-6">Computadores que servem outros</p>
                <p class="text-center mb-6"><strong>Ex: Linux Server, Windows Server</strong></p>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li>✅ Hospedam sites e serviços</li>
                    <li>✅ Alta estabilidade</li>
                    <li>✅ Ex: GitHub Pages roda aqui</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Embarcados -->
            <div class="card bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-8">
                <div class="icon-circle bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-400 mx-auto mb-6">🤖</div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-2">Embarcados</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-orange-400 mb-6">Sistemas Embutidos</p>
                <p class="text-center mb-6"><strong>Ex: TV, Carro, Micro-ondas</strong></p>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li>✅ Dentro de outros dispositivos</li>
                    <li>✅ Recursos limitados</li>
                    <li>✅ Faz apenas uma tarefa específica</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-16 text-gray-400">
            <p>MOCHILA • Desenvolvido por LUCAS • Ipaba, MG • 2026</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
